---------------- ESCAPE COMMANDS ----------------- CURSOR COMMANDS        SCREEN COMMANDS J  cursor <--          U   Scroll up one line L  cursor -->          M   Scroll down one line I  cursor up           O   Scroll up one screen ,  cursor down         .   Scroll down one screen K  cursor <-- then --> 7   Scroll left Y  cursor word <--     9   Scroll right [  cursor word -->     P   Go to page # TEXT BLOCK COMMANDS    PROGRAM MODES F  Find string         ;   insert text R  Replace string      /   go to supervisor mode ^  Insert one char.    1   go to overwrite mode }} Marker characters   ESC Editor mode W  withdraw saved text S  save text from cursor to marker D  duplicate (without withdrawing) saved text Z  zap (delete) text from cursor to marker